snippet.title: Cursed Travels: Sunken City - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a dark journey, filled with puzzles, riddle, and skeletons, in search for the mysterious Sunken City. Releasing on Steam *eventually*!

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1498070/Cursed_Travels_Sunken_City/

Based on the highly-rated Cursed Travels web games, which can be played right here: https://ferociter.itch.io/
Follow me on Twitter for semi regular updates: https://twitter.com/CasperVDommelen
